      "id": "PopularPost200075",
      "post_content": "This card's actually pretty much a bamf in limited. 3/3 flier for 5 is good (not phenomenal, but good) and his ability to boost your other little guys like [Moon Heron](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Moon Heron), [Lantern Spirit](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lantern Spirit) and the [Midnight Haunting](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Midnight Haunting) tokens into very relevant attackers is great.  \n  \nHe won't win you the game on his own back, but his body will go a long way towards getting you there itself, and the ability stapled on to him can go miles as well.",
